autodiff:
Label of button to enable or disable [https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Krinkle/Tools/Real-Time_Recent_Changes#AutoDiff AutoDiff]. This feature automatically loads the next diff in the list, after marking a change as patrolled.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|next}}

asc:
Label of the radio button that sets sort order to ascending.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|Rtrc-desc}}

cvn-adder-empty:
Placeholder text for when the author is unknown.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-cvn-adder}}
{{Identical|Unknown}}

cvn-reason-empty:
Placeholder text when no reason was found

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-cvn-reason}}

desc:
Label of the radio button that sets the sort order to descending.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|Rtrc-asc}}

filter:
Section label for various change filters.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-filter-hideliu}}
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-filter-hidebots}}
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-filter-unpatrolled}}
{{Identical|Filter}}

filter-unpatrolled:
Label of the checkbox to hide patrolled edits, showing only unpatrolled edits.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|rcshowhidepatr}}

help:
Label for button to enable or disable "Help" pointers in the program.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-helpicon-tooltip}}
{{Identical|Help}}

lastupdate-cvn:
Foot note showing when the CVN database was last updated. Parameters:
* $1 - timestamp
{{Identical|Last update}}

lastupdate-rc:
Foot note showing when the list of changes was last refreshed from the server. Parameters:
* $1 - timestamp
{{Identical|Last update}}

skip:
Label of button that will skip an item in the list of changes.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-skippededit}}
{{Identical|Skip}}

typeEdit:
Label of the checkbox to include changes that edit existing pages.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|Rtrc-typeNew}}
{{Identical|Edit}}

typeNew:
Label of the checkbox to include changes that create new pages.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|Rtrc-typeEdit}}
{{Identical|New page}}

unskip:
Label of the button that removes a change from the list of changes to skip and adds it back to the regular list of changes.

See also:
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-skip}}
* {{msg-intuition|rtrc-skippededit}}
